       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. TODPAY.
      *WORKING WELL
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.

           SELECT TARGET-FILE ASSIGN TO TARGET
               ORGANIZATION IS INDEXED
               ACCESS MODE IS DYNAMIC
               RECORD KEY IS T-LOAN-ID
               FILE STATUS IS FS1.

           SELECT PAID-FILE ASSIGN TO PAIDOUT
               ORGANIZATION IS SEQUENTIAL
               ACCESS MODE IS SEQUENTIAL
               FILE STATUS IS FS2.

           SELECT PAY-FILE ASSIGN TO PAYMENT
               ORGANIZATION IS INDEXED
               ACCESS MODE IS SEQUENTIAL
               RECORD KEY IS P-TRANS-ID
               FILE STATUS IS FS3.

           SELECT DELQ-FILE ASSIGN TO DELQOUT
               ORGANIZATION IS SEQUENTIAL
               ACCESS MODE IS SEQUENTIAL
               FILE STATUS IS FS4.

       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.

       FD TARGET-FILE.
       01 TARGET-REC.
          05 T-LOAN-ID    PIC X(6).
          05 T-CUST-ID    PIC X(5).
          05 T-NAME       PIC X(10).
          05 T-STATUS     PIC X(8).
          05 T-ACT-AMT    PIC 9(6).
          05 T-AMT-PAID   PIC 9(6).
          05 T-PAY-TYPE   PIC X.
          05 T-YORN       PIC X.
          05 T-BEST       PIC X(37).

       FD PAY-FILE.
       01 PAY-REC.
          05 P-TRANS-ID   PIC X(11).
          05 P-LOAN-ID    PIC X(6).
          05 P-CUST-ID    PIC X(5).
          05 P-NAME       PIC X(10).
          05 P-STATUS     PIC X(8).
          05 P-ACT-AMT    PIC 9(6).
          05 P-AMT-PAID   PIC 9(6).
          05 P-PAY-TYPE   PIC X.
          05 P-YORN       PIC X.
          05 P-BEST       PIC X(26).

       FD PAID-FILE RECORDING MODE IS F.
       01 PAID-REC.
          05 PAID-DATA PIC X(80).

       FD DELQ-FILE RECORDING MODE IS F.
       01 DELQ-REC.
          05 DELQ-DATA PIC X(80).

       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-EOF1      PIC X VALUE 'N'.
       01 WS-EOF2      PIC X VALUE 'N'.
       01 FS1          PIC XX.
       01 FS2          PIC XX.
       01 FS3          PIC XX.
       01 FS4          PIC XX.
       01 WS-DATE      PIC X(10).
       01 WS-ACT-AMT   PIC Z(6).
       01 WS-PAID-AMT  PIC Z(6).

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.

       MAIN-PARA.

           OPEN I-O TARGET-FILE
                INPUT PAY-FILE
                OUTPUT PAID-FILE DELQ-FILE

           IF FS1 NOT = '00'
              DISPLAY 'ERROR OPEN TARGET: ' FS1
              STOP RUN
           END-IF

           IF FS3 NOT = '00'
              DISPLAY 'ERROR OPEN PAY: ' FS3
              STOP RUN
           END-IF

      *--- STEP 1: UPDATE TARGET ---*

           PERFORM UNTIL WS-EOF1 = 'Y'

              READ PAY-FILE
                 AT END
                    MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF1
                 NOT AT END
                    PERFORM UPDATE-TARGET
              END-READ

           END-PERFORM

           CLOSE TARGET-FILE
           OPEN INPUT TARGET-FILE

           IF FS1 NOT = '00'
              DISPLAY 'ERROR REOPEN TARGET: ' FS1
              STOP RUN
           END-IF

      *--- POSITION FILE ---*

           MOVE LOW-VALUES TO T-LOAN-ID

           START TARGET-FILE KEY >= T-LOAN-ID

           IF FS1 NOT = '00'
              DISPLAY 'START FAILED: ' FS1
              MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF2
           END-IF

      *--- WRITE HEADERS ---*

           PERFORM WRITE-HEADERS

      *--- STEP 2: SPLIT FILE ---*

           PERFORM UNTIL WS-EOF2 = 'Y'

              READ TARGET-FILE NEXT
                 AT END
                    MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF2
                 NOT AT END
                    PERFORM SPLIT-REC
              END-READ

              IF FS1 NOT = '00' AND FS1 NOT = '10'
                 DISPLAY 'READ ERROR: ' FS1
                 MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF2
              END-IF

           END-PERFORM

           CLOSE TARGET-FILE PAY-FILE PAID-FILE DELQ-FILE

           STOP RUN.

      *--- UPDATE TARGET ---*

       UPDATE-TARGET.

           MOVE P-LOAN-ID TO T-LOAN-ID

           READ TARGET-FILE KEY IS T-LOAN-ID

           IF FS1 = '00'
              MOVE P-YORN     TO T-YORN
              MOVE P-AMT-PAID TO T-AMT-PAID

              REWRITE TARGET-REC

              IF FS1 NOT = '00'
                 DISPLAY 'REWRITE FAILED: ' T-LOAN-ID
              END-IF

           ELSE
              DISPLAY 'NOT FOUND: ' P-LOAN-ID
           END-IF.

      *--- SPLIT RECORD ---*

       SPLIT-REC.

           IF T-YORN = 'Y'
              PERFORM WRITE-PAID
           ELSE
              PERFORM WRITE-DELQ
           END-IF.

      *--- WRITE PAID ---*

       WRITE-PAID.

           MOVE SPACES TO PAID-DATA

            MOVE T-ACT-AMT  TO WS-ACT-AMT
            MOVE T-AMT-PAID TO WS-PAID-AMT

           STRING
             T-LOAN-ID  ' '
             T-CUST-ID  ' '
             T-NAME     ' '
             T-ACT-AMT  ' '
             T-AMT-PAID ' '
             T-PAY-TYPE
             DELIMITED BY SIZE
             INTO PAID-DATA
           END-STRING

           WRITE PAID-REC.

      *--- WRITE DELQ ---*

       WRITE-DELQ.

           MOVE SPACES TO DELQ-DATA
           MOVE T-ACT-AMT  TO WS-ACT-AMT
           MOVE T-AMT-PAID TO WS-PAID-AMT

           STRING
             T-LOAN-ID  ' '
             T-CUST-ID  ' '
             T-NAME     ' '
             T-ACT-AMT  ' '
             T-AMT-PAID
             DELIMITED BY SIZE
             INTO DELQ-DATA
           END-STRING

           WRITE DELQ-REC.

      *--- HEADERS ---*

       WRITE-HEADERS.
           MOVE FUNCTION CURRENT-DATE(1:10) TO WS-HDATE
           MOVE WS-HDATE TO PAID-REC(70:10)
           MOVE 'PAID REPORT' TO PAID-DATA
           WRITE PAID-REC

      *    MOVE WS-HDATE TO DELQ-REC(70:10)
      *    MOVE 'DELINQUENCY REPORT' TO DELQ-DATA
      *    WRITE DELQ-REC

           MOVE 'LOANID CUSTID NAME ACT-AMT PAID-AMT TYPE'
                TO PAID-DATA
           WRITE PAID-REC

      *    MOVE 'LOANID CUSTID NAME ACT-AMT PAID-AMT'
      *         TO DELQ-DATA
      *    WRITE DELQ-REC.
